Introduction


An Old Moon (Korean: 그믐; Japanese: そんな) is a Korean rock band, under 그믐, consisting of 5 members: Choi Goeun, Kim Kyoungsup, Go Chang Young, Lee Ji-Nam and Lee Jun Mo. The band debuted on November 10, 2017, with the album “The day I fell asleep during the day (낮에 잠든 날).“
